metadata.name: Rainbow City
metadata.description:
Shot taken in Thailand, with the original rainbow sky just before sunrise.

I was surprised when I disect the color and found the real colors was very stand out shown as the rainbow gradient.
This shot has taken from the very rare spot and private in Thailand. I was lucky to have carried the 200-600G lens.

Gear : A7S3 + 200-600G 

Full printing size will be sent after purchase.
